  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe the general characteristics of friction</item>
<item>List the various types of friction</item>
<item>Calculate the magnitude of static and kinetic friction, and use these in problems involving Newton&#8217;s laws of motion</item>
</list></md:abstract>
